  <bodyText><![CDATA[<h2>Austria Ski Holidays by Rail</h2>
<p>Ride the rails straight to Austria's snowy peaks. Experience stunning alpine views, first-class resorts, and a journey that is as memorable as the destination itself.</p>
<div class="c-tabs-beta__content-table--row-wrapper">
<p><img src="/media/13063687/skiing-in-collado-near-formigal-in-spain.jpg" alt="austriaresorts" data-udi="umb://media/537b89dd52ea4b838d5074c10fdc3182" /></p>
<h3>Travel to Austria by Rail</h3>
<p>See what St Anton has in store for you this winter out on the slopes - jump on the train to <a data-udi="umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb}" title="Austria">Austria</a> this ski season with an Inghams ski package holiday.</p>
<p>If scenic routes to snowy summits and spacious, relaxed travel appeals to you, then we've just the ticket.</p>
<p>Ready for the red runs? Book online by selecting London St Pancras for departure or <a data-udi="umb://document/e5b8abf94a554299a3960566b88e9193" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e5b8abf94a554299a3960566b88e9193}" title="Contact Us">contact us</a> to find out more. </p>
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><em>(New 2024/25 train time details coming shortly)</em></h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a rel="noopener" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/search-results?/search-results?to=[CH]&amp;from=QQS" target="_blank" title="Rail deals" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center" data-anchor="?/search-results?to=[CH]&amp;from=QQS">View Austria Rail Deals</a></p>
